metadata.name: D-Psyche No.1 #1
metadata.description:
Drops in the shape of water droplets, question the source of life, life and death, through the circulation of water, fire, earth and air. If water is viewed as a fundamental element that can create and penetrate all states of matter, time, and space, then the drops chosen by the artist can be the fundamental element of life and death, and furthermore, the fundamental element of artistic formation. 

#NFTart  #Drops
